  <brief_title>Acceptance and Commitment Therapy With Vestibular Rehabilitation for Chronic Dizziness</brief_title>
  <official_title>Acceptance and Commitment Therapy With Vestibular Rehabilitation for Chronic Dizziness: a Randomized Controlled Trial</official_title>
